          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Does Google penalise PBNs?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. Google issues both algorithmic and manual penalties for PBN use. Manual penalties can result in complete deindexation of both PBN sites and the money site they link to. Google's spam team actively identifies and devalues PBN link signals.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">How does Google detect PBNs?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Google identifies PBNs through shared hosting footprints, identical WHOIS data, similar site structures, unnatural anchor text patterns, low-quality thin content, and link velocity anomalies. Manual reviewers also identify PBN patterns during link scheme audits.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Are PBNs ever worth the risk?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. Short-term ranking gains from PBNs are frequently reversed by algorithm updates or manual actions. The risk-reward ratio is negative: you can lose rankings built over years when a penalty lands. White-hat link building through content, PR, and partnerships produces durable results.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What should I do if a past SEO agency used PBNs on my site?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
