            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Run a backlink audit using Ahrefs or SEMrush. Identify domains that share footprints — shared hosting, thin content, unnatural anchor text. Disavow those links via Google Search Console's disavow tool, then file for reconsideration if a manual penalty exists.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

